pting to give music back to the people...music that has conviction and a story...music that gives good feelings and drives positive emotions...music that you aren&rsquo;t afraid your children will listen to. \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nWe love giving people a STORY again! <br />\r\nLOVE not LUST, HAVING FUN, &ldquo;GOOD-TIMES&quot; &amp; CHERISHED MEMORIES not &ldquo;THROW YOUR GUN&rsquo;S IN THE AIR YOU N&rsquo;S B&rsquo;S &amp; W&rsquo;S, &amp; SPANK &ldquo;DAT&rdquo; _ _ _ <br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou may be asking yourself &quot;why is he trying to change something that no one cares about&quot;. Good question. First, I CARE &amp; I grew up &ldquo;old school&rdquo; where there wasn&rsquo;t any software to make you sound good. Second, we here at Weezie Productions are sick of the degrading, no class, disgusting language &amp; racial overtones in this industry today. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nI know I may sound a little negative, but there is good music&hellip;no, there&rsquo;s GREAT music out there, you just have to find it. Unfortunately it&rsquo;s not always easy to find, based on what radio is forcing us to listen to.<br />\r\nYou have to go to the internet, live shows, and local club &ndash; get out and see, live, and breath music as it was meant to be.&nbsp; Who knows, maybe we&rsquo;ll even see a change in society!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSo what if you&rsquo;re fat, short, over 16 years old, too tall, got one leg and a kick stand&hellip;Can You Sing without technology helping you sound perfect?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYES! Fans, there is software out there that you can sing into and it will make the worst of singers sound good, so the next time you throw your money at the next exciting flavor radio pushes on you. Think to yourself, how much is really coming from the artist and how much is coming from the software being used AND is it worth paying $100.00 or more for a ticket to see it in concert.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI&rsquo;m not implying that we here at Weezie Production have the best voices in the world, but you can bet your life it&rsquo;s real and natural. All we ever use is a mic to get the music to you - which was how it was done when it all made sense and made a difference in our lives. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe want to get back to music for people who want songs with meaning, a feeling, soul, and fun. <br />\r\nEven though we will never see another Luther Vandross Weezie Productions refuses to add to the insanity that&rsquo;s making it to mainstream radio. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe all have to die doing something with our time, and this is how we plan to spend our time. We&rsquo;re giving the 30-40-50 year olds there options back.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEnjoy and we appreciate everyone&rsquo;s continued support. Tell everyone you know to check it out and support Weezie...We can&#39;t do it without you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe hope you feel good by the end of the CD and want to listen to it over and over again. \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\nWeezie Productions was founded in 2005 and is focused on new artists with a positive message. They are currently working and collaborating on several new projects with some of today&rsquo;s hottest producers and singers &ndash; a group of fresh, mature singers and producers who are dedicated to changing the negative adolescent nature of today&rsquo;s music. \r\n</p>\r\n',0,'',0,''),(2289,540,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',1,'',0,''),(2292,667,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',1,'',0,''),(2293,717,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',1,'',0,''),(2294,722,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',1,'',0,''),(2295,728,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',1,'',0,''),(2296,769,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',1,'',0,''),(2297,771,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',1,'',0,''),(2298,796,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',1,'',0,''),(2299,801,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',1,'',0,''),(2300,1815,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',1,'',0,''),(2301,1813,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',1,'',0,''),(2302,1808,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',1,'',0,''),(2303,1804,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',1,'',0,''),(230