ists! <br />\r\nThe Song &#39;Slippin Away&#39; has not only been downloaded online during the last year more than 29,000 times, but has more recently been chosen by <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.ascap.com/\">ASCAP</a> for excellence in song writing at the ASCAP Music Expo 07 in L.A. <br />\r\nDownload sales on digital sites such as iTunes and Rhapsody have remained strong, as have Material Worldwide CD sales from our <a type=\"0\" href=\"http://www.9lies.net/9liesmerchshop.html\" target=\"_blank\">Online Music Store</a>, and all of this is down to you! Thank you!!! <br />\r\nIt doesn&#39;t end there though! The new album &#39;Halfway from Nowhere&#39; is almost finished and sounding absolutely fantastic!! If you haven&#39;t already done so, then join the <a type=\"0\" href=\"http://www.9lies.net/contact9lies.html\" target=\"_blank\">9Lies Mailing list</a> for free, to be kept up to date and receive free member offers! <br />\r\nClick <a type=\"3\" href=\"http://www.9lies.net/9liesfreemusic.html\" target=\"null\">here for Free Downloads</a> of 5 broadcasts from The &#39;Behind It All&#39; Album, including &#39;Slippin Away&#39;, &#39;Behind It All&#39;, &#39;Blind&#39;, &#39;Too Late&#39; and &#39;The Gap&#39;<br />\r\nFor additional resources about the band, check out the following links!<a type=\"0\" href=\"http://www.myspace.com/99lies\" target=\"_blank\"> MySpace Music</a> ,<a type=\"0\" href=\"http://www-9lies-net.bebo.com/\" target=\"_blank\">9Lies BEBO</a>, <a type=\"0\" href=\"http://phobos.apple.com/WebObjects/MZStore.woa/wa/viewAlbum?playListId=167653808\" target=\"_blank\">9Lies on iTunes</a>, <a type=\"0\" href=\"http://www.9lies.net/venafestivallodz07.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.9lies.net/venafestivallodz07.html</a>, and <a type=\"0\" href=\"http://www.purevolume.com/9lies\" target=\"_blank\">9</a><a type=\"0\" href=\"http://www.reverbnation.com/9lies\" target=\"_blank\">L</a><a type=\"0\" href=\"http://www.indie911.com/index.php?cID=33441\" target=\"_blank\">I</a><a type=\"0\" href=\"http://cdbaby.com/cd/9lies\" target=\"_blank\">E</a><a type=\"0\" href=\"http://www.decentx.com/artist.asp?id=4725\" target=\"_blank\">S</a><a type=\"0\" href=\"http://www.airplaydirect.com/music/9lies\" target=\"_blank\">-</a><a type=\"0\" href=\"http://www.jamendo.com/en/album/6685\" target=\"_blank\">0</a><a type=\"0\" href=\"http://www.last.fm/music/9Lies/+wiki\" target=\"_blank\">7</a> <a type=\"0\" href=\"http://www.fuzz.com/fan/9Lies\" target=\"_blank\">.</a> Or visit - <a type=\"0\" href=\"http://www.9lies.net/\" target=\"_blank\">The home of Alternative Indie Rock Band 9Lies</a><br />\r\n<font size=\"2\" color=\"#cc0000\"></font><a href=\"..//\" title=\"SUBSCRIBE\" class=\"nav\"></a></font>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font size=\"-0\"><a href=\"http://www.9lies.net/\" class=\"navgrey\"></a></font>\r\n</p>\r\n',1,'<div align=\"left\">\r\n<p align=\"center\">\r\nStevie Mann - Lyrics / Lead Vocals // Dave Kernohan - Guitars // Nick Black - Guitars // Chris Cardwell - Bass // Stephen McAuley - Drums\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n',0,''),(2427,1000180,'DEVANIA',9,43,'http://WWW.MYSPACE.COM/DIVANIAC','RALEIGH, NC','919 332 9849','<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" class=\"MsoBodyText\">\r\n<strong>Just imagine yourself being immersed in beautiful musical and lyrical songs.&nbsp; Cheniqua Gardiner also known, as &ldquo;DEVANIA&rdquo; is a fascinating and talented performing artist whose music experiences reflect her Neo-Soul and Opera genres. She was born and raised in the Bahamas. Her musical experiences were developed at a very young age when she began singing in children&rsquo;s&rsquo; choirs and the <em>&ldquo;The Bahamas Baptist Heavenly Voices.&rdquo; </em>&nbsp;The choir received numerous honors and awards.&nbsp; </strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n<strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: black\">At the age of fifteen, she joined The Bahamas National Youth Choir (a world renowned touring choir that traveled extensively through-out Europe and Asia)&nbsp;under the directorship of <em>Mr. Cleophas R.E Adderley</em> (Director of Culture) where she continued to develop into a versatile singer and performer. During her tenure with the choir, she traveled to Canada, Trinidad, Tabago and various Family Islands in the Bahamas.&nbsp; She has appeared as a soloist with The National Youth Choir and University of Miami Symphony Orchestra during the Choir&rsquo;s Fifth Anniversary presentation of the &ldquo;Nelson&rdquo; Mass by Haydn where she has had the privilege to sing for the Governor General (the Right Honorable Sir Orville Turnquest) of the Bahamas.&nbsp;</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0pt\" class=\"MsoBodyText\">\r\n<strong>Devania was barely eighteen years old and, her rich voice was equivalent with that of more mature seasoned soloists.&nbsp; It was during this time that she was recognized by the critics in the music society to have been a child prodigy as far as her music ability was concerned.&nbsp; As a result, she was offered music scholarships at <em>Florida</em><em> International University, University of Miami, (Miami Fl. respectively) Morgan State University (Baltimore (Maryland), Texas Woman&rsquo;s University (Denton, Texas) and Saint Augustine&rsquo;s college (Raleigh, N.C) just to name a few</em>.&nbsp; Devina has broadened her horizons and is currently recording her new album as a Neo-Soul R&amp;B artist.&nbsp; She is currently working with Grier &amp; Associates Entertainment whose expertise with artist development is guiding her in the right direction on her path to being a great artist.&nbsp; With all of her experiences as an opera singer one can just imagine what she is about to unleash as a Neo-Soul R&amp;B singer.</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n',0,'',0,''),(2428,1000184,'Hype Boiiz',3,20,'http://www.myspace.com/officalhypeboiiz310page','4361 fenmore, waterford, MI','(248)-877-7819','<div ali